{"id":602761,"date":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":15}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"80","ytitle":"","mtitle":"吾侪何忍失斯人","ftitle":"——悼赵丹","authors":["杜宣"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜宣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋云漠漠映空庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噩耗传来我大惊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剧影两坛称祭酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画书双杰树奇旌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南冠二度君多难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩劫十年病此根；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是河清海宴日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吾侪何忍失斯人?"}]}